Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.67,0:00:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你好\N{\fs20}Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.12,0:00:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我是博士\N{\fs20}I'm the Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.46,0:00:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,现在 很多人问我\N{\fs20}Now, a lot of people have asked me,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.57,0:00:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我是怎么让自己看起来这么酷的\N{\fs20}how I managed to look so cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.50,0:00:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 其实并不是很多人\N{\fs20}Well, not...not actually a lot of people
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.60,0:00:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,他们用的也不是"酷"这个词\N{\fs20}and they didn't use the word "cool"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.82,0:00:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,也不是任何其他词语\N{\fs20}or any of the other words.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.80,0:00:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,因为从来没有人问过我这个问题\N{\fs20}Because no one's ever asked me that at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.24,0:00:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,但如果他们问我\N{\fs20}But if they had asked me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.90,0:00:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我会用一个字来回答\N{\fs20}I'd have answered with one word,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.97,0:00:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我的衣服\N{\fs20}My clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.00,0:00:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,尤其是领结和有时会戴的毡帽\N{\fs20}Especially the bow-tie and a fez sometimes,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.12,0:00:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,公平地说 这不是一个字\N{\fs20}which in fairness is several words.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.32,0:00:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,但这是因为我很激动\N{\fs20}but that's because I'm excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.55,0:00:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 很激动\N{\fs20}Yes, excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.25,0:00:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,今天 为了"帮助儿童"特别节目\N{\fs20}Today, for Children in Need,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.92,0:00:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我要送出我身上的衣服\N{\fs20}I am giving the clothes off my back!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.62,0:00:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我的夹克\N{\fs20}My jacket.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.60,0:00:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,全宇宙独一无二\N{\fs20}Unique in the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.32,0:00:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,由无限多的粗花呢制成\N{\fs20}Made of infinity tweed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.45,0:00:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,如果这件夹克被任何子弹或激光击中\N{\fs20}If this jacket is hit by any kind of bullet or laser beam
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.32,0:00:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,甚至是被三重折叠的量子强化忍者武器击中\N{\fs20}or even a triple enfolded quantum strengthened ninja staff
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.45,0:00:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,那它就彻底毁了\N{\fs20}It would be completely ruined.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.09,0:00:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,所以请对它小心点\N{\fs20}So please be careful with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.05,0:00:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我的领结\N{\fs20}My bow-tie.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.47,0:00:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,领结现在是 将来也一直是很酷的\N{\fs20}Bow-ties are and always will be cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.91,0:00:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我的衬衫\N{\fs20}My shirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.98,0:01:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,看起来像一件普通的衬衫\N{\fs20}Looks like an ordinary shirt,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.85,0:01:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,摸起来像一件普通的衬衫\N{\fs20}feels like an ordinary shirt,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.83,0:01:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,其实就是\N{\fs20}is in fact,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.20,0:01:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,一件普通的衬衫\N{\fs20}an ordinary shirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.50,0:01:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我的裤子\N{\fs20}My trousers.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.42,0:01:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不是普通的裤子\N{\fs20}Not just any old trousers.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.20,0:01:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,超级裤子\N{\fs20}Hyper trousers!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.70,0:01:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,与普通裤子非常相似\N{\fs20}Very similar to normal trousers,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.85,0:01:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,但是名字里面有个"超级"\N{\fs20}but with word hyper in front.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.35,0:01:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我的靴子\N{\fs20}My boots.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.22,0:01:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,一只\N{\fs20}One.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.87,0:01:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,两只\N{\fs20}Two.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.97,0:01:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,三只!\N{\fs20}Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.65,0:01:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 时间领主\N{\fs20}Oh! Time Lords.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.65,0:01:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我们总是充满惊喜\N{\fs20}We are full of surprises.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.32,0:01:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,现在\N{\fs20}Now,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.50,0:01:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你们中有谁想要竞标\N{\fs20}if any of you would like to bid for
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.00,0:01:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这些完全独一无二的衣服\N{\fs20}these completely unique items of clothing,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.00,0:01:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,链接正在显示在你的屏幕上\N\N\N\N{\fs20}the URL is appearing on your screens right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.72,0:01:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不 别担心 这些不是真的衣服\N\N\N\N{\fs20}No, no. Don't worry, these aren't my real clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.10,0:01:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,这些是全息影像衣服\N\N\N\N{\fs20}These are hologram clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.02,0:01:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,请不要碰遥控器上的红色按钮\N\N\N\N{\fs20}Please don't touch the red button on your remote,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.12,0:01:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,否则它们会消失的\N\N\N\N{\fs20}or they might just disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.62,0:01:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 不! 住手!\N\N\N\N{\fs20}Ah, no! Stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.02,0:01:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,住手!\N\N\N\N{\fs20}Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.75,0:01:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 朋友们 我需要转移一下注意力\N\N\N\N{\fs20}Okay guys, I'm going to need a diversion.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.92,0:02:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,快放预告片!\N\N\N\N{\fs20}Run the trailer!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.67,0:02:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,英国 1941年\N{\fs20}England, 1941.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.47,0:02:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,战争正在打响\N{\fs20}And there's a war on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.82,0:02:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,这里闹鬼吗\N{\fs20}Is it haunted?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.20,0:02:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你是谁?\N{\fs20}Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.12,0:02:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,通常被叫做"博士"\N{\fs20}Usually call the Doctor,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.25,0:02:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,或者"管理员"\N{\fs20}or the Caretaker,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.15,0:02:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,或者"滚出这个星球"\N{\fs20}or get off this planet
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.22,0:02:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,那个人简直太荒唐了\N{\fs20}That man is quit ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.10,0:02:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道!\N{\fs20}I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.30,0:02:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,离他远点\N{\fs20}Stay away from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.62,0:02:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么你房间里放了个电话亭\N{\fs20}Why we got a phone box in your room?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.11,0:02:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是电话亭 这是我的衣柜\N{\fs20}It's not a phone box, it's my wardrobe.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.87,0:02:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你弟弟他在哪\N{\fs20}Your brother, where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.72,0:02:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 来吧\N{\fs20}Okay, Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.80,0:02:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在哪里\N{\fs20}Where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.90,0:02:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,在客厅里的盒子里的森林里\N{\fs20}In forest in a box in a sitting room.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.02,0:02:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,现在的学校都是怎么教你们的\N{\fs20}What do they teach you in school these days?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.67,0:02:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,这片森林十分不对劲\N{\fs20}There is something very wrong in this forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.12,0:02:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,而你弟弟现在正在森林中间呢\N{\fs20}And your brother is right in the middle of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.55,0:02:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,史上最棒的圣诞节\N{\fs20}Best Christmas ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.82,0:02:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\fs20}I know.
